      "role": "user",
      "content": "wait i think i got confused. i thought the circle was used to find the relative major of a minor key, not the other way around. so if i'm looking at c minor, how do i use the circle to find its relative major? can u step me through the actual movement on the circle? like if i'm at c minor, which direction do i move and how many steps?",
